name: eos_heavy_semantic_drift
intended:
hostname leaf-01
interface Ethernet1
   description uplink-spine-a
   mtu 9214
   ip address 192.0.2.2/31
   no shutdown
router bgp 65000
   router-id 10.255.255.1
   neighbor 192.0.2.1 remote-as 65100
   neighbor 192.0.2.1 description spine-a
   address-family ipv4
      network 10.10.1.0/24
      neighbor 192.0.2.1 activate
ip access-list ACL-EDGE-IN
   10 permit tcp 10.10.1.0/24 any eq https
   20 permit tcp 10.10.1.0/24 any eq ssh
   90 deny ip any any log
actual:
hostname leaf-01
interface Ethernet1
   ip address 192.0.2.2/31
   mtu 9214
   description uplink-spine-a
   shutdown
router bgp 65000
   neighbor 192.0.2.1 description spine-a
   router-id 10.255.255.1
   neighbor 192.0.2.1 remote-as 65100
   address-family ipv4
      neighbor 192.0.2.1 activate
      network 10.10.1.0/24
ip access-list ACL-EDGE-IN
   20 permit tcp 10.10.1.0/24 any eq ssh
   10 permit tcp 10.10.1.0/24 any eq https
   90 deny ip any any log
